title: BONUS EPISODE: Real Talk w/ Tisha Campbell On Moving Forward, Martin, Putting Yourself First + Success
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Actress Tisha Campbell joins Ebro in the Morning for an enlightening and passionate conversation on moving forward especially after disappointment and divorce, putting yourself first, dating later in life, the 'Martin' reunion, and much more! She stars in the new sitcom 'Uncoupled' alongside Neil Patrick Harris. It premieres on Netflix on July 29! #EbrointheMorning #HOT97 #TishaCampbell
